    {
      "id": 100,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## SLO / Error Budget &nbsp;—&nbsp; *czy dotrzymujemy obietnicy?*\n\n**SLO:** 99.5% requestów bez 5xx **i** 99.5% requestów < 500 ms, w oknie **30 dni**. &nbsp;·&nbsp; **Error budget** = 0.5% = ~3.6 h/mies.\n\n> Panele *30d* (górny wiersz) liczą stałe okno 30 dni i **ignorują** time-picker. Wykresy historyczne i burn-rate reagują na zakres czasu. Próg latencji = `le=\"0.5\"` (granica bucketa SLO — patrz `application.yml`)."
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Availability SLO — compliance 30d",
      "description": "Procent requestów HTTP bez błędu serwera (5xx) w ostatnich 30 dniach. Zielony ≥ 99.5% (SLO).",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 4, "w": 6, "h": 6 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "(1 - (sum(increase(http_server_requests_seconds_count{job=~\"$job\",status=~\"5..\"}[30d])) / clamp_min(sum(increase(http_server_requests_seconds_count{job=~\"$job\"}[30d])), 1))) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "success %",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "decimals": 3,
          "min": 99,
          "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "#f43f5e", "value": null },
              { "color": "#f59e0b", "value": 99.5 },
              { "color": "#10b981", "value": 99.9 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "graphMode": "none",
        "colorMode": "background_solid",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false }
      }
    },

